name: Sētā tengu to Kamen inu
description: Sētā trap people who are cold by lighting fires in the forests in winter. She sends Kamen inu after those who try to escape. If the Kamen catches them, he takes off his mask and drags the people who  are frozen in front of his true face and takes them back to Sētā. The two are rumored to be a couple in their other lives.
